e0 ng\u01b0ng \u0111\u01a1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o ti\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ebfn qu\u00fd v\u1ecb. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb d\u1ed3n \u0111\u01a1n th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m gi\u00e1p t\u1ebft, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i xin ch\u1ec9 ra m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 l\u00fd do qu\u00fd v\u1ecb n\u00ean c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi v\u1ed9i v\u00e0ng th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n:<\/p>\n<h3><strong>1 \u2013 C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 sai s\u00f3t trong thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf khi th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea5p g\u00e1p<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p>T\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn T\u1ebft Nguy\u00ean \u0110\u00e1n th\u00ec ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n h\u01a1n 2 th\u00e1ng, do \u0111\u00f3, n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng trong th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea9y nhanh c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u1ec3 d\u00e0nh th\u1eddi gian cho vi\u1ec7c thi c\u00f4ng. Do \u0111\u00f3, v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u1eb7p sai s\u00f3t trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 tr\u00e1nh kh\u1ecfi, \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng kh\u00e2u th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n sau \u0111\u00f3.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a1411e4 elementor-column elementor-col-33 elementor-top-column\" data-id=\"a1411e4\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap\">\n<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/section>\n<section class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-826c836 elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default elementor-section elementor-top-section\" data-id=\"826c836\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-co