ata-id=\"66e0989\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n<h3><strong>2 \u2013 Ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u k\u1ef9 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u t\u1eeb ph\u00eda gia ch\u1ee7<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p>V\u1edbi ti\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf v\u00e0 thi c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng, \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1, tr\u00f2 chuy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 trao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a ra ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n h\u1ee3p l\u00fd nh\u1ea5t, h\u01a1n n\u1eefa, v\u1edbi phong c\u00e1ch c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n h\u00f3a Bespoke l\u00ean ng\u00f4i, kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eeda \u0111\u1ed5i theo nhu c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ngay c\u1ea3 khi \u0111ang thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf.<br \/>\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p ph\u1ea3i thi c\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 g\u1ea5p, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn r\u1eb1ng kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ed1t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch nhanh ch\u00f3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n, c\u00e1c KTS c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 mong mu\u1ed1n t\u1eeb ph\u00eda ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0.<\/p>\n<h3><strong>3 \u2013 Kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9 thi c\u00f4ng<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p>N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 thi c\u00f4ng trong th\u1eddi gian qu\u00e1 ng\u1eafn, ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd b\u1ecb gi\u1ea3m \u0111i \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3, \u00edt c\u00f3 \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb n\u00e0o \u201cd\u00e1m\u201d \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o v\u1edbi qu\u00fd v\u1ecb v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c b\u00e0n giao m\u1ed9t s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cao ngay c\u1ea3 trong th\u1eddi gian thi c\u00f4ng g\u1ea5p g\u00e1p. Ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m gi\u1ea3m s\u00fat s\u1ebd l\u00e0m m\u1ea5t \u0111i uy t\u00edn c\u1ee7a ch\u00ednh \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb \u0111\u00f3 tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/section>\n<section class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-00dd991 elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default elementor-section elementor-top-section\" data-id=\"00dd991\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2823ec6 elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column\" data-id=\"2823ec6\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-191e506 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"191e506\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n<div class=\"elementor-image\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/donggia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/phong-ngu-hien-dai.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/donggia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/phong-ngu-hien-dai.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/donggia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/phong-ngu-hien-dai-300x169.jpg 300w, https:\/\/donggia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/phong-ngu-hien-dai-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/donggia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/phong-ngu-hien-dai-1024x576.jpg 1024w\" alt=\"phong-ngu-hien-dai\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" \/><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/section>\n<section class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-fad1a16 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default elementor-section elementor-top-section\" data-id=\"fad1a16\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5f121be elementor-column elementor-col-33 elementor-top-column\" data-id=\"5f121be\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3e0103a elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"3e0103a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n<h2><strong>L\u1ee2I TH\u1ebe C\u1ee6A KH\u00c1CH H\u00c0NG KHI THI C\u00d4NG SAU T\u1ebeT<\/strong><\/h2>\n<p>B\u1edfi v\u1eady, qu\u00fd v\u1ecb h\u00e3y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng th\u00f4ng minh khi t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb uy t\u00edn, b\u00e0y t\u1ecf nguy\u1ec7n v\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ra th\u1eddi gian th\u00edch h\u1ee3p v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o ti\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho vi\u1ec7c thi c\u00f4ng n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t.<br \/>\n\u0110\u1ed3ng Gia s\u1ebd tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi: \u201cThi c\u00f4ng n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t sau T\u1ebft c\u00f3 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd? Kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ee3i g\u00ec?\u201d<\/p>\n<h3><strong>1 \u2013 KTS c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u nh\u1eefng m\u1eabu thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf m\u1edbi<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p>N\u1ebfu l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn thi c\u00f4ng n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t sau T\u1ebft, qu\u00fd v\u1ecb s\u1ebd l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt v\u00e0 s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng theo xu h\u01b0\u1edbng <strong>thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t<\/strong>\u00a0m\u1edbi. C\u00e1c KTS c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u nh\u1eefng m\u1eabu thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t v\u00e0 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho t\u1eebng kh\u00f4ng gian theo \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1 t\u00ednh c\u1ee7a gia ch\u1ee7.<\/p>\n<h3><strong>2 \u2013 \u0110\u01a1n v\u1ecb thi c\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ed1t<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p>C\u00e1c \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb thi c\u00f4ng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn v\u00e0 nh\u1eadp v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng ngu\u1ed3n v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cao \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t trong n\u0103m m\u1edbi. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00edch c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ebfn l\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c gia \u0111\u00ecnh sau khi b\u00e0n giao s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-17eeb94 elementor-column elementor-col-33 elementor-top-column\" data-id=\"17eeb94\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap\">\n<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/section>\n<section class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7370785 elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default elementor-section elementor-top-section\" data-id=\"7370785\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap